{"type": "article", "id": 22878, "title": "带尺子的圆珠笔", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-26T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144113hbXNkGt9WYluQfER.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一杆结合了尺子的圆珠笔，来自日本设计师 Shigeru Ban（坂茂）。笔身是铝合金制的三角，上面有不同比例的刻度，很适合建筑师等人使用。它分为上下两截，转动笔身可以使笔尖露出。精细刻度搭配灰色的几何笔杆让它成为一杆很酷的笔。售价 90 美元，<a href=\"http://acmestudio.com/products-writing_tools-collezione_materiali/Shigeru_Ban/SCALE_Retractable_Roller_Ball/SCALE_GRAY%7C/P2SB01RB/\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021441116R0M5JTNkUBlbi7Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144112ek69DFZjXbWPOSVY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144112t7au3PFLr10S6JUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}